modules.description: This module enables user authentication via public key registration and verification workflows, utilizing P256 cryptographic keys with support for FIDO-U2F and "none" attestation formats. It processes data structures such as challenges, credential identifiers, and attestation responses to facilitate secure key exchange and cryptographic validation, primarily for web-based services integrating hardware tokens or platform-level security modules. The implementation focuses on decoding, verifying, and transporting authentication data while requiring external storage for managing registered credentials and session state.
